If I create a link like this: 

{noformat}
[foo | http://www.atlassian.com/foo]
{noformat}

An unwanted space appears between the text and the link icon. Also, the "outgoing links" section ends up with two entries for this link, one of them with a trailing "\]"!

The case with no whitespace (\[foo|http://www.atlassian.com/foo]) works fine.
